headline: CRISPR Therapeutics Stock Could Double Your Money, According to Wall Street. Is It Time to Buy?
summary: CRISPR Therapeutics stock is down more than 80% from the peak it reached in 2021.  The first drug from CRISPR Therapeutics launched early last year, but annualized sales are still less than $60 million.  CRISPR Therapeutics recently reported promising early-stage clinical trial results for a cholesterol-reducing treatment.
